# This directory is the PENDING queue for the cataloging pipeline.
#
# Three-directory model:
#   static/queue/      — PENDING. Files awaiting promotion.
#   static/in-flight/  — IN_PROGRESS. The file currently being cataloged.
#   static/originals/  — CATALOGED. Completed files stay here permanently.
#
# Files arrive here from three sources: the web upload form
# (functions/api/upload.ts), the MCP server's acquire_for_catalog tool,
# and direct git pushes. All three converge on the same queue, and the
# catalog workflow promotes one file at a time in FIFO order.
#
# Files in this directory are eligible for deletion via the queue-delete
# endpoint (functions/api/queue/delete.ts), exposed in the Acquisition
# page UI as PENDING-row checkboxes. Once a file is promoted to
# static/in-flight/, it can no longer be removed via that path.
